ed, 03 Jul 2024 13:38:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/germany-stops-planned-sale-vws-gas-turbine-business-china-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾参议员在 Tiktok 上声称中国导弹计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-senator-makes-tiktok-claim-about-china-missile-plans-2024-07-03/</link><description>菲律宾一位著名参议员在社交媒体上表示，她知道中国计划用高超音速导弹瞄准菲律宾，这引起了轰动，尽管国家安全委员会表示不知道任何此类安全威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:58:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-senator-makes-tiktok-claim-about-china-missile-plans-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>Formula E关注中国选手周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/formula-e-has-eyes-chinas-zhou-2024-07-03/</link><description>电动方程式首席执行官杰夫·多兹 (Jeff Dodds) 表示，如果周冠宇在赛季结束后失去一级方程式赛车的席位，他希望周冠宇能够参加全电动锦标赛。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/formula-e-has-eyes-chinas-zhou-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟报告详述了中国对经济的广泛干预</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-report-details-widespread-chinese-interference-economy-2024-07-03/</link><description>在宣布对中国制造的电动汽车征收临时关税之前，欧盟委员会于 4 月发布了一份长达 712 页的报告，内容涉及中国政府向国内企业提供的多层补贴。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-report-details-widespread-chinese-interference-economy-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>英国大选：工党的外交政策计划是什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-election-what-are-labours-foreign-policy-plans-2024-07-03/</link><description>英国工党预计将赢得周四的全国大选，在野14年后重新掌权，并任命凯尔·斯塔默(Keir Starmer)为英国新任首相。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:23:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-election-what-are-labours-foreign-policy-plans-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，俄罗斯公司提高锌产量以满足政府需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/russian-firms-raise-zinc-output-meet-government-demand-sources-say-2024-07-03/</link><description>两位知情人士告诉路透社，俄罗斯企业在过去一个月提高了锌金属产量，以受益于国家需求的增长，并减少对中国作为材料目的地的依赖。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/russian-firms-raise-zinc-output-meet-government-demand-sources-say-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>普华永道在监管审查中任命新中国区主管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pwc-names-new-china-head-amid-regulatory-scrutiny-2024-07-03/</link><description>普华永道 (PwC) 任命内部高管李彦宏为新任中国区主管，此举正值该公司面临中国大陆和香港金融监管机构的调查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:48:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pwc-names-new-china-head-amid-regulatory-scrutiny-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯央行每日人民币掉期交易量创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-central-banks-daily-yuan-swap-volume-hits-record-high-2024-07-03/</link><description>数据显示，俄罗斯央行周三在货币互换交易中向银行提供了创纪录的195亿元人民币（26.8亿美元），因为在美元和欧元交易受到限制后，银行寻求其他方式来补充其外汇储备。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:43:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-central-banks-daily-yuan-swap-volume-hits-record-high-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：工作岗位扫描新纪录，特斯拉股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-03/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:05:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>独家：印度官员参观富士康 iPhone 工厂，询问高管招聘事宜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/indian-officials-visit-foxconn-iphone-plant-question-executives-about-hiring-2024-07-03/</link><description>在路透社报道苹果主要供应商拒绝已婚女性从事 iPhone 组装工作后，一名官员表示，印度劳工官员本周参观了该国南部的一家富士康工厂，并向高管询问了该公司的招聘做法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/indian-officials-visit-foxconn-iphone-plant-question-executives-about-hiring-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，德国阻止了大众燃气轮机业务向中国出售的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/germany-blocks-planned-sale-vws-gas-turbine-business-china-sources-2024-07-03/</link><description>两位政府消息人士称，德国内阁周三阻止了大众汽车子公司曼能源解决方案公司燃气轮机部门向一家中国公司出售的计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:32:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/germany-blocks-planned-sale-vws-gas-turbine-business-china-sources-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>北京与欧盟进行谈判，中国电动汽车制造商准备应对关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-makers-brace-tariffs-beijing-eu-engage-talks-2024-07-03/</link><description>随着欧盟委员会对中国制造的电动汽车征收临时关税的时间紧迫，汽车制造商正准备迎接数十亿美元的新成本，分析师预计这些成本将减缓其在欧洲的扩张。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:32:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-makers-brace-tariffs-beijing-eu-engage-talks-2024-07-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>